<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173022>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Esperiopsis flagrum sp. nov. a, Holotype in situ at 955 m depth in Amchitka Pass. b, holotype after collection. c, Long fusiform styles and microscleres. d, Microscleres overview: large and small categories of isochelae and sigmas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173022/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173023>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Esperiopsis flagrum sp. nov. a, backside of large isochela. b, Small isochela. c, Side view of small isochela. d, Large and small sigmas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173023/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

